The MakerSpace Developer’s Documentation¶

This is the documentation for the MakerSpace API. It is divided into sections based on functionality. Each page documents for each endpoint, the endpoint url, the permissions, the parameters, and a brief description. The models page has specifications for all the objects that will be passed.
